title: Jacks takes stunning catch to remove Smith
subtitle: Will Jacks "comes up with something special" to dismiss Steve Smith, taking a brilliant diving catch at backward square leg as Australia fall to 292-5 on day two of the second Ashes Test.
full_text: Will Jacks "comes up with something special" to dismiss Steve Smith, taking a brilliant diving catch at backward square leg as Australia fall to 292-5 on day two of the second Ashes Test.
